questions.quote: Carol? I was just wondering if Joey could ask you a question about breast-feeding?
Oh it was perfect! I mean it really felt like he was my friend again.

Hello? Yeah, this is she. Oh! You're kidding! You're kidding! Oh thank you! I love you!
